Edit po ulet: thank you po ulet sa walang sawang support guys pero tumawag yung kapatid ko po from Cebu, wala na daw po si mama. I don't know what to do, I'm supposed to take the psychometrician board examination this September 24 and 25. My flight should be this 3:55 am. Pero I just received the most heartbreaking news. Please pray for us still. Thank you.

Edit: Hello po, on behalf of my family, we would like to extend our heartfelt gratitude to you guys for extending your generosity to us, especially po kay Mama. Your financial help and prayers are very helpful sa situation po namin ngayon. Grabeng trials po talaga pero lalaban parin para kay mama. We may not be able to thank you personally, but please know that we appreciate your help po. Maraming maraming salamat po ulit 🙏🥺.

Para sa mga nais pang mag share ng extra money po nila, maaari po kayong mag send sa:

📌 Gcash: 09954688823
📌 Account name: Riezel Joy Villajuan 

Hello OPC, Good morning! 

I am Riezel Joy Villajuan, an alumna (2025 graduate) dito sa FEU. Baka lang po pwedeng makalapit sa inyo, dahil nangangailangan po kami ng tulong financial sa ngayon. Nagbabakasakali lang po ako kung sakaling may maiaabot kayong extra amount of money, kahit maliit pero malaking tulong na po, para pampa-hospital po ng mama ko.

She is a CKD Stage 5 patient but refused to undergo dialysis kasi alam niya sa sarili niya na hindi niya kakayanin. She was hospitalized last August 2024 at kahit kaunti ay gumaan ang kanyang pakiramdam, alam po namin na dialysis talaga ang kailangan kapag may CKD. Kaya lang, naubos na po ang maliit naming ipon at napilitan na kaming mangutang sa mga kakilala. Ngayon, sobrang manas na manas na talaga si Mama. Kailangan po ulit siyang maipatingin sa doctor, pero sadly, wala na po kaming sapat na pera. Kaya po, I am humbly asking for your financial help. Any amount will do po maliit man o malaki. Napakalaking bagay na po para sa amin. Thank you po for your understanding and prayers. God bless po 🙏

message.text:
Edit po ulet: thank you po ulet sa walang sawang support guys pero tumawag yung kapatid ko po from Cebu, wala na daw po si mama. I don't know what to do, I'm supposed to take the psychometrician board examination this September 24 and 25. My flight should be this 3:55 am. Pero I just received the most heartbreaking news. Please pray for us still. Thank you.

Edit: Hello po, on behalf of my family, we would like to extend our heartfelt gratitude to you guys for extending your generosity to us, especially po kay Mama. Your financial help and prayers are very helpful sa situation po namin ngayon. Grabeng trials po talaga pero lalaban parin para kay mama. We may not be able to thank you personally, but please know that we appreciate your help po. Maraming maraming salamat po ulit 🙏🥺.

Para sa mga nais pang mag share ng extra money po nila, maaari po kayong mag send sa:

📌 Gcash: 09954688823
📌 Account name: Riezel Joy Villajuan 

Hello OPC, Good morning! 

I am Riezel Joy Villajuan, an alumna (2025 graduate) dito sa FEU. Baka lang po pwedeng makalapit sa inyo, dahil nangangailangan po kami ng tulong financial sa ngayon. Nagbabakasakali lang po ako kung sakaling may maiaabot kayong extra amount of money, kahit maliit pero malaking tulong na po, para pampa-hospital po ng mama ko.

She is a CKD Stage 5 patient but refused to undergo dialysis kasi alam niya sa sarili niya na hindi niya kakayanin. She was hospitalized last August 2024 at kahit kaunti ay gumaan ang kanyang pakiramdam, alam po namin na dialysis talaga ang kailangan kapag may CKD. Kaya lang, naubos na po ang maliit naming ipon at napilitan na kaming mangutang sa mga kakilala. Ngayon, sobrang manas na manas na talaga si Mama. Kailangan po ulit siyang maipatingin sa doctor, pero sadly, wala na po kaming sapat na pera. Kaya po, I am humbly asking for your financial help. Any amount will do po maliit man o malaki. Napakalaking bagay na po para sa amin. Thank you po for your understanding and prayers. God bless po 🙏

📌 Para sa nais mag-abot ng tulong:
